Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.00,0:01:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.04,0:01:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你不要忘记我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.17,0:01:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.01,0:01:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.58,0:01:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.88,0:01:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天就会回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.61,0:01:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用不着哭成这样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.42,0:01:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是说啊 葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去做法事 只要住一天就够了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.52,0:01:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.79,0:01:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车子已经来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.16,0:01:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 葵大小姐 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.29,0:02:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.83,0:02:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷 我们不在的时候就麻烦你看家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.70,0:02:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以自由使用这栋房子 没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.34,0:02:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.81,0:02:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.54,0:02:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.65,0:02:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第九话  一夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衣服都洗完了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.67,0:02:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜学姊还在睡吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.67,0:02:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算说是遇到了在九州时的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎么样 五瓶一升的烧酒也太多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.58,0:02:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且大部分好像都是蒂娜喝掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.22,0:03:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球在全速旋转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.42,0:03:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.13,0:03:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是稍微去看看比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题 没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要过一会儿 马上又会生龙活虎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.93,0:03:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电话 我先离开一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.88,0:03:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过是小葵跟雅都不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房屋就感觉特别的大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.22,0:03:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 那还是有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.12,0:03:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.93,0:03:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…其实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.77,0:03:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 那我们走吧 水无月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,铃木？佐藤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们来的真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.37,0:03:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是才刚挂断电话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.41,0:03:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚的电话是你们打的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 就是在玄关前打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水无月 去换上这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.19,0:04:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.09,0:04:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐藤 刚刚那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.92,0:04:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摄影大会啦 摄影大会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摄影大会？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.87,0:04:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电车？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.07,0:04:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个165系的纪念列车在仓敷奔驰着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.37,0:04:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那个长距离型的165系啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.34,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会因为这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.78,0:04:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而燃烧的人要去哪里找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.95,0:04:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.45,0:04:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐藤 你应该不是小铁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.92,0:04:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 佐藤副社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.49,0:04:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.53,0:04:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Great！水无月 敬礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 敬礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Perfect！Brilliant！（完美！出色！）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.07,0:05:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是偶像扮演一日站长的极至啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一日站长？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.98,0:05:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 你知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是我照纪念列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.55,0:05:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后佐藤用列车当背景来照一日站长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,单独去旅行不是太无聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓在家靠父母 出外靠朋友啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.89,0:05:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂 就是为了那种事情就把妙子带去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么叫做“那种事情”啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 事情就是这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.36,0:05:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天就会回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是为了成为摄影师的第一步啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又被骗去了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.28,0:05:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天？不就是要住一天吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.51,0:05:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动作真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是骗我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.46,0:05:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,记忆 记忆已经开始消失了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.23,0:06:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子下去 我对你的记忆也终究会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要！我不要这样！阳介！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夕子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真无聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子好饿喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东 妙子 我要吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.98,0:06:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵跟雅为了做法事回家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子则是被骗去仓敷参加摄影旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.23,0:06:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜你的早餐放在冰箱里喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.87,0:06:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那现在这里只有我跟阿薰两个人而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.57,0:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说的确…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我们两个人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么了？阿薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的脸很红喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.26,0:07:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 没有…其实…什么都没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在动摇什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙 我在想什么啊 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情应该不会变得那么奇怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷静点 冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想出来吗？不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果随便放你出来 雅又会生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.45,0:07:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.82,0:07:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 你来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？蒂娜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.19,0:07:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于还是放弃做菜了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.66,0:07:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么啊 真没礼貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 有什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.63,0:07:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 帮我挽一下袖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.57,0:07:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,袖子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.73,0:07:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为手都湿了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.90,0:07:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 快点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 是 那么你先转过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快点就要湿掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从后面捲啦 快点快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从后面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.39,0:08:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.06,0:08:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.89,0:08:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我要为阿薰做出好吃的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷声响彻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔神 吼叫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜身上发出的味道好香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.94,0:08:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙 我又在胡思乱想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.14,0:08:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久等了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明太子意大利面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到你会做这么正经的料理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就做你想象中的东西给你吃好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.69,0:08:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.46,0:08:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃 真好吃啊 这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.09,0:08:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 好 那我也来吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜你可以做出这种料理的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.93,0:08:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个人生活也没有问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.11,0:09:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你难道不明白我的心情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.71,0:09:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂…蒂娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家觉得每天做饭很麻烦嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.30,0:09:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜 浴室没人用喔 你先去洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.07,0:09:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浴室是空的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加斯卡马…吼叫吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.61,0:09:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,击退地球上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？你不是去浴室了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊 就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.65,0:10:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要进来之后就没什么了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.13,0:10:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有…有点没办法冷静呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.82,0:10:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我就先来唱一首歌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.89,0:10:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷声响彻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.66,0:10:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔神 吼叫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,击退地球上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.33,0:10:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有邪恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了 停电了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.97,0:11:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.57,0:11:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,配电盘在哪里啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.01,0:11:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 我不知道要到哪里去找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.48,0:11:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 蒂娜她没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.44,0:11:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么暗真危险…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.58,0:11:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.39,0:11:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这啥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.83,0:12:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜 在的话回答我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.63,0:12:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.60,0:12:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好怕 我好怕喔 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜 她…她不是裸体吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 等一下 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要等啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要等啥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.52,0:12:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂蒂蒂蒂娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.16,0:12:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之 因为不知道配电盘在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.36,0:12:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来今天应该是不会好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.16,0:12:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要拿着这个蜡烛就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以回你房间去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.11,0:12:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.31,0:12:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我讨厌这么黑嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.88,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要一个人睡啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.55,0:12:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下啊 蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚我要跟阿薰一起睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起?喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 我不要放开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是    不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子就能安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.52,0:13:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜已经起来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.09,0:13:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总算是保持住理性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟小葵的时候是很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.66,0:13:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟蒂娜时更是另外一种煎熬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拖她的福还真是睡不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.47,0:13:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早…早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.34,0:13:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍等一下 我马上就把饭做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天晚上谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为阿薰称赞所以我又做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.21,0:14:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.41,0:14:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚起来哪吃得下明太子意大利面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么 我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.92,0:14:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,配电盘进水的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有走火真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.76,0:14:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.47,0:14:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下去神社吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.13,0:14:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神社？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.48,0:15:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫阳花市集啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜中将
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.78,0:15:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了吗？阿薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.15,0:15:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是个天才啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.87,0:15:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有好多东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 去那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.18,0:15:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里？投香油钱的地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想摇那个“喀啦喀啦”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“喀啦喀啦”？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.98,0:15:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行的啦 人这么多挤不进去的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 我要摇“喀啦喀啦”啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用现在去也可以的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.69,0:15:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想摇“喀啦喀啦”啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.63,0:15:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你这么想要摇啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.70,0:16:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为小时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.97,0:16:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟爸爸妈妈一起摇过后就没有再摇过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.51,0:16:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且那个时候我也没有好好的许愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.78,0:16:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 我无论如何还想再摇一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.60,0:16:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想摇“喀啦喀啦”对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧 蒂娜 把你所想的全部摇下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.68,0:16:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望全地球都能幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.12,0:16:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么奇怪的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.89,0:16:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 你在笑什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.14,0:17:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.14,0:17:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 有什么奇怪的嘛 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.61,0:17:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以说是真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.65,0:17:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰你变了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.39,0:17:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们初次见面的那个时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.46,0:17:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.23,0:17:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.07,0:17:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么说呢 好像很寂寞的样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.77,0:17:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉不让任何人进入心中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.24,0:17:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.74,0:17:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 我才邀你进摄影社啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？我曾经那样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 就是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.85,0:18:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我总是注意着你 所以我很明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是因为搬到这里的缘故吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东和管理员都是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会让人觉得心情很愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.96,0:18:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我是美国人 也不会对我另眼看待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.00,0:18:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇到困难的事情 也会认真的帮忙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.34,0:18:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直就是像是真的一家人一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.28,0:18:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是个很厉害的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东她的脾气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么样的家事都会做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个就叫做大和抚子吧？（日本具有传统美德的女性）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.73,0:18:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要经历什么样的生活…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能变成那个样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.67,0:18:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真想生为房东那样子的日本人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这样的话…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.05,0:19:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.05,0:19:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 喝吧 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.05,0:19:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜 好 来喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.73,0:19:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 钿女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.49,0:19:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钿女也喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂 不能把钿女放出来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛 不要说这么小气的话啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.63,0:19:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行的事情就是不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.00,0:19:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说的话阿薰你就是不喝啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 那是我的啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜学姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.37,0:19:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.77,0:20:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵你回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.74,0:20:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰你在这种地方睡的话会感冒的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.55,0:20:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.98,0:20:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜 先回去房间了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…话说回来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅…雅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.33,0:20:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.40,0:20:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这到底是怎么回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钿女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.81,0:20:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷 我的确是说过你可以自由使用这栋房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.81,0:20:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是把钿女放出来是绝对不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.72,0:20:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要给我装傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.42,0:20:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罚你现在起清理这里 还有打扫整个房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.29,0:20:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在开始？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.79,0:20:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是从现在开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.26,0:20:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.66,0:20:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.00,0:20:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.47,0:21:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始给我打扫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.90,0:21:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要给我抱怨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.67,0:21:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 放开我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.41,0:21:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要揉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的…蒂娜学姊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.28,0:21:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
